{"Id":812278,"Title":"瑞鹤仙·题章式之四当斋勘书图。饥读之以当肉，寒读之以当裘，孤寂读之以当友朋，幽忧读之以当金石琴瑟，宋尤之语也。饥以当食，渴以当饮，诵之可以当韶頀，览之可以当夷施，明胡元瑞语也。皆藏书家故实，式之取以名斋。为题此阕","Dynasty":"清","Author":"夏孙桐","Context":"冷芸温旧绪。只有涯生事，书城容据。穷通自天赋。几寒虫声咽，舂锄心苦。铅晨椠暮。笑吾侪、长镵托付。兴来时叶扫云披，万陷女娲能补。何许。嫏嬛仙境，入画幽栖，吴峰如雾。他年指顾。隐君莫著书处。任虞渊残景，津桥余恨，尽入零缣剩蠹。看裒然、向录千秋，碧藜烟古。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"瑞鹤仙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"e536e7c87e0a4f031120e518a97e053c","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5797737,"Sentence":"冷芸温旧绪。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lěng yún wēn jìu xù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797739,"Sentence":"穷通自天赋。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qióng tōng zì tiān fù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797741,"Sentence":"铅晨椠暮。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiān chén qiàn mù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797744,"Sentence":"何许。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hé hǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797746,"Sentence":"他年指顾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tā nián zhi gù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":9,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797747,"Sentence":"隐君莫著书处。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yin jūn mò 著shū chǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797740,"Sentence":"几寒虫声咽，舂锄心苦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī hán chóng shēng yān ，chōng chú xīn kǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797742,"Sentence":"笑吾侪、长镵托付。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiào wú chái 、cháng chán tuō fù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797745,"Sentence":"嫏嬛仙境，入画幽栖，吴峰如雾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"láng qióng xiān jìng ，rù huà yōu qī ，wú fēng rú wù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5797748,"Sentence":"任虞渊残景，津桥余恨，尽入零缣剩蠹。","R